column5: May you all have a great time.Play safe and I,ll be thinking of the great time I missed.  Looking forawrd to the reports on yer returns.  Be safe all.
thanks  For those about to FISH, we salute you  We FISH at dawn on the front line Like a bolt right out of the blue The sky's alight with the WALLEYE bite Heads will roll and rock tonight
Dang.. now he's a poet !  Thanks Brian....
Terry either your losing weight or you have done something with your hair???...anyways ...what MissFish said....have fun all !
come on guys  you must know the song I change 2 words
Is it from the 'oldies' station?  For those about to rock - fire We salute you For those about to rock, we salute you Those about to rock - fire We salute you Fire We salute you We salute you
Go to SLEEP.You gotz to get up soon.
Yah.. about noon. I'm pickin him up at 2:15 Brian ! lol
now if it was Lloyd...it would be 4:15.............................am  a few of the other guys 4:20................
Well thanks Brian !Perhaps we will see you next year.  Ok I better go to bed I am getting up at 3:30am Lew oclock.  Blast off time is 4am  I will be back in 4 days.  MTP

I am going down for the day on SATURDAY with a friend . Anyone know where the best place to fish from shore would be????  Down by the ferry docks is my best thought.  WHERE would be the best place to meet up with some of you OFNers  . I would like to see some of the catch that comes in. I have only fished the bay in the spring so I am comming down to check it out for next fall. IF its as good as they say I will be there with my boat next year.   THANKS and good luck to all.  PS   IF anyone has room for two in there boat  we would be only to glad to pay our share for a shot on the bay. GOOD luck and play safe.  MR. PIKE
Hve fun, I'll be thinking of you while I hang the Christmas lights and other stuff...
Lloyd probably has room on his morning charter before picking up Terry, Wayne and Dano for the afternoon run.
Thanks for the best wishes, Brian.  I'll do me best to look after dat brudder o' yers.  Jes' headin' out the door.
Yup.. I hope everyone has a blast.. think big pickerel!!
